Subject: [PATCH] fix: v1.44.6 - remove electron package.json type:module +
 bundle all core subpaths

Root cause: ReferenceError: require is not defined in ES module scope
1. electron/package.json had "type":"module" -> Node loaded CJS main.js as ESM
2. checkpoint/rules/utils kept external -> runtime require(ESM) failed

Fixes:
- Restored correct electron/package.json (no type:module, proper deps)
- Removed checkpoint/rules/utils from external in build-main.cjs
- All @codepilot/core subpaths now bundled into main.js as CJS
